<section id="work" class="zg-section">
  <div class="zg-grid">
    <h2>we are the sum of our experiences</h2>
    <h3>here are some of the highlights...</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="zg-grid">
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><a href="https://www.OpenConf.com/"><img src="images/oc.png" alt="OpenConf" title="visit the OpenConf web site" /></a></p>
	<p>Developer of the <b>OpenConf</b> peer-review, abstract, and event management web application used by thousands of events and journals in over 100 countries and supporting more than a dozen languages. Available both licensed for client installation and Cloud/<abbr title="Software-as-a-Service">SaaS</abbr>-based.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/wh2.jpg" alt="White House detail" /></p>
	<p>Adviser to the <b>White House</b> on cross-agency collaboration, innovation, identity, emerging technologies, open data and open science. Invited lecturer at the National Defense University and other venues on topics ranging from cybersecurity and blockchain to artificial intelligence and machine learning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/obs3.jpg" alt="map of project deployment area" /></p>
	<p>Integrated and deployed the highest <span style="white-space: nowrap;">Wi-Fi</span> link in the northeastern United States across 8 KM of backcountry and powered by solar in support of remote sensing for the <b>Mount Washington Observatory</b>. Also, developed, hosted and managed the Observatory's web site receiving millions of daily hits.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
   <div class="zg-grid">
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/dot.jpg" alt="Treasury building" /></p>
	<p>Innovation expert at the <b>U.S. Department of the Treasury</b> leading and facilitating efforts on governance, critical infrastructure, cybersecurity, fintech, blockchain, and distributed ledger.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/amc.jpg" alt="snapshot of phenology mapping application" /></p>
	<p>Developed a volunteer management system and map-based plant monitoring application for the <b>Appalachian Mountain Club</b> within a legacy hosting environment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/catf.jpg" alt="cloud and sky photo" /></p>
	<p>Designed, developed, hosted, and managed the <b>Clean Air Task Force</b> public, intranet, and extranet web sites, including creating an interactive map application of diesel soot health impacts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
 <div class="zg-grid">
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/bilat.jpg" alt="partial project home page" /></p>
	<p>Developed bilingual, web-based information infrastructures for <b>U.S. Department of Defense</b> collaboration with counterparts in the Korean and Japanese defense forces.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/proc.jpg" alt="procurement cover page" /></p>
	<p>Trained cross-functional procurement teams from the <b>Federal Bureau of Investigation</b> and the <b>U.S. Department of the Treasury</b> on product strategy and visioning for agile digital acquisition.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/un.jpg" alt="UN building with flags" /></p><!-- CC BY 2.0 senhormario@Flickr -->
	<p>Developed the first web-based machine language translation service, initially as a prototype for the <b>United Nations</b> and later deployed on U.S. Intelligence networks, supporting 10 languages.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="zg-grid">
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/ic.jpg" alt="CIA World Factbook map" /></p>
	<p>Led the design and deployment of a multi-national information sharing network among the intelligence components of seven countries and served as technical liaison for <b>U.S. Intelligence Community</b> delegation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/cms.png" alt="services architecture diagram" /></p>
	<p>Technical team lead and adviser for the assessment and architecting of <b>Center for Medicare and Medicaid Services</b>' Reporting Hospital Quality Data for Annual Payment Update (RHQDAPU), Continuity Assessment Record & Evaluation (CARE), Enterprise Identity Services (EIDM), and Enterprise Shared Services (ESS).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="zg-width-one-third item">
	<p><img src="images/training.jpg" alt="training session photo" /></p>
	<p>Trained programmers, designers, <abbr title="quality assurance">QA</abbr> analysts, researchers, and procurement specialists on secure web application development practices at over a dozen events including <b><abbr title="Association for Computing Machinery Conference on Computer and Communications Security">ACM CCS</abbr>, <abbr title="Applied Computer Security Applications Conference">ACSAC</abbr>, <abbr title="Open Web Application Security Project">OWASP</abbr> AppSec, <abbr title="Information Security Summit">ISS</abbr>, and <abbr title="Conference on Privacy, Security and Trust">PST</abbr></b>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
